text: Val de Bagnes is a municipality in Entremont in the canton of Valais in Switzerland. It is named after the valley of the same name. On 1 January 2021, the former municipalities of Bagnes and Vollèges merged to form the new municipality of Val de Bagnes.Amtliches Gemeindeverzeichnis der Schweiz - Angekündigte Änderungen 2020 - Ausgabe vom 17.
